Module bestSokobanEverV6

This module use Java JDK 15.0.1, JavaFX 15 and JUnit4 is used for tests

  • Packages

    Opens
    Package Description
    controller
    The package contains GameController class, which handles user input and communicates with game model
    data
    This package offers key data structures in the game (i.e. level, grid and record)
    factory
    This package offers Factory for basic game objects, to support Factory design patten.
    main
    This package offers the start of the game
    model
    This package offers model for the game, to support mvc design pattern.
    object
    This package offers basic objects in the game (wall, floor, keeper...), by inheriting GameObject class.
    viewer
    This package offers the viewer of the game, to support MVC design pattern.
